&lt;li&gt;Assist&amp;nbsp;and enable C3 AI&#39;s customers to build their own applications on the C3 AI Suite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the design and implementation of new features of the C3 AI Suite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyse model performance across asset fleets, diagnose issues such as&amp;nbsp;low risk&amp;nbsp;scores or false positives, and recommend hyperparameter adjustments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with data and subject matter experts from C3 AI and its customer teams to seek, understand, validate, interpret, and correctly use new data elements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
