&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s in computer science, Electrical Engineering, Statistics, Operations Research or equivalent fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; Applied Machine Learning experience (regression and classification, supervised and unsupervised learning). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
