&lt;li&gt;Assist&amp;nbsp;and enable C3 AI&#39;s customers to build their own applications on the C3 AI Suite.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the design and implementation of new features of the C3 AI Suite.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
