&lt;li&gt;Analyze model performance across enterprise deployments, diagnose issues such as poor recall or false positive rates, and recommend targeted improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with data engineers and subject matter experts from C3 AI and customer teams to source, validate, and correctly leverage new data assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
