&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MS or PhD in Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Statistics,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Operations Research, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
